description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

Dr. Fauci rejects Clay and Buck's invitation to appear on the show. Trudeau reelected despite emergence of new blackface photos. Psaki, Harris and the Biden administration are lying about the fabricated narrative of border agents whipping migrants. Doocy asks Psaki if Biden has never been to the border. Fauci's office contacts us again after we called him out on his rejection of our invitation.
